  "bezeichnung": "Digital Image Processing 1 - in Englisch",
  "kreditpunkte": 4,
  "lernziele": "<p>Digital Image Processing 1 and Digital Image Processing 2 form together a one-year introductory sequence into modern digital image processing</p>",
  "vorausgKenntnisse": "<ul><li>Fundamental knowledge of multivariable calculus</li><li>Fundamental knowledge of Fourier analysis</li><li>Fundamental knowledge of probability theory</li><li>Fundamental knowledge of linear algebra</li><li>Solid command of the English language, since the lectures are in English</li></ul>",
  "semesterBewertung": "keine Note oder Wertung",
