      "id": 28162,
      "kuerzel": "DigPro1Engl",
      "bezeichnung": "Digital Image Processing 1",
      "lernziele": "<p>At the end of the module the students are expected to understand the following concepts and be able to apply them to real world image processing problems:</p><ul><li>Digital Image Fundamentals</li><li>Image Enhancement in the Spatial Domain</li><li>Image Enhancement in the Frequency Domain</li><li>Image Restoration</li><li>Color Image Processing</li></ul>",
      "planinhalt": "<p>The module is structured as follows:</p><ul><li>Digital Image Fundamentals</li><li>Image Enhancement in the Spatial Domain</li><li>Image Enhancement in the Frequency Domain</li><li>Image Restoration</li><li>Color Image Processing</li></ul><p>Note that changes to the above plan are possible and will be communicated in class</p>",
